OL,3,CBridgend hospital's roof repairs to
OL,4,Ccost #20m as building faces #40m
OL,5,Cbacklog
OL,7,FRepairing the rotting roof at the
OL,8,FPrincess of Wales Hospital in Bridgend
OL,9,Fhas been estimated to cost around
OL,10,F#20million.
OL,12,FCwm Taf Morgannwg University Health
OL,13,FBoard chief executive Paul Mears
OL,14,Fdiscussed the challenges the hospital
OL,15,Fis facing at a Bridgend County Borough
OL,16,FCouncil meeting held on 23 October.
