OL,7,FThe health board declared a critical
OL,8,Fincident at the start of October after
OL,9,Fit said a survey discovered rot in the
OL,10,Fbeams which support the roof, with
OL,11,Falmost 200 patients initially affected
OL,12,Fand the hospital's operations affected.
OL,14,FSpeaking at the meeting CEO Mears
OL,15,Fdescribed how the roof was found to be
OL,16,Fdegraded after an intrusive survey,
OL,17,Fwith roofing batons rotted and
OL,18,Fcompletely disintegrated in some
OL,19,Fplaces, leaving around 10,000 square
OL,20,Fmetres of roofing "completely
OL,21,Fcompromised".
