OL,7,FHe added that negotiations were now
OL,8,Funderway to finalise a contract for
OL,9,Fthe work to be carried out at the
OL,10,Fsite, which would hopefully see a
OL,11,Fphased completion starting in November
OL,12,F2024 and finishing by the summer of
OL,13,F2025.
