OL,7,FIt was also revealed in the meeting
OL,8,Fthat a previous survey that had been
OL,9,Fcarried out on the roof in 2019 had
OL,10,Fshowed "significant risk" with its
OL,11,Fconcrete tiles reaching the end of
OL,12,Ftheir life. Councillor Ian Spiller
OL,13,Fsaid: "If you've had a report done in
OL,14,F2019 which highlights a significant
OL,15,Frisk, surely you plan for this in
OL,16,Ffuture budgets and surely if you know
OL,17,Fthat there's a problem you do
OL,18,Feverything you can to mitigate it."
