OL,7,FThe chief executive responded by
OL,8,Fsaying that with only around #8m worth
OL,9,Fof capital allocation across all of
OL,10,Fits facilities in the health board
OL,11,Farea each year, and a #40million
OL,12,Fbacklog of maintenance issues at the
OL,13,FPrincess of Wales Hospital alone,
OL,14,Fpriorities of how to use resources had
OL,15,Fto be made.
OL,17,FIt was also noted that the health
OL,18,Fboard is now speaking with Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment for funding towards the
OL,20,Festimated #20m needed to carry out the
OL,21,Ffull roof replacement.
