OL,7,FAt the meeting, Mr Mears also
OL,8,Fapologised for the disruption which
OL,9,Fhas been caused to both staff and
OL,10,Fpatients in the area.
OL,12,FHe said: "I would very much be happy
OL,13,Fto apologise to staff who've had a lot
OL,14,Fof disruption to deal with on a daily
OL,15,Fbasis, the patients and their families
OL,16,Fwho've been disrupted, and also the
OL,17,Fwider community who have clearly been
OL,18,Fimpacted."
