OL,7,FIt comes after one worker at the
OL,8,Fhospital, who we are calling "Sarah",
OL,9,Ftold ITV Wales she has seen "dead
OL,10,Fbirds, vegetation and tomato plants"
OL,11,Fgrowing in the hospital's guttering,
OL,12,Fand claimed that the rotting roof, and
OL,13,Fits consequences, were worse than what
OL,14,Fwas disclosed publicly by Cwm Taf
OL,15,FMorgannwg University Health Board. The
OL,16,Fhealth board strong denies those
OL,17,Fclaims.
